<div class="title">Soma and the Divine Lady Have a Night Out</div>
<div class="substance">Amanita muscaria & Salvia divinorum</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Silver_Strigoi_Vii&Exact=1">Silver_Strigoi_Vii</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Silver_Strigoi_Vii. "Soma and the Divine Lady Have a Night Out: An Experience with Amanita muscaria & Salvia divinorum (exp21762)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 19, 2005. erowid.org/exp/21762</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
